The largest Chinese companies are united against Alibaba
Chinese companies, including the largest commercial real estate developer in China Dalian Wanda Group and Internet giants Tencent Holdings (social networks, messengers, etc.) and Baidu (the largest Chinese search engine), create a company that will compete in the online trading market with Alibaba.
